---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import portrait from '../assets/martin-opedal.jpg';
---
<section id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-label">Profile</span>
    <h2>About</h2>
    <div class="about-grid">
      <Image
        src={portrait}
        alt="Portrait of Martin Opedal, Lead Cloud Solution Architect at Microsoft"
        widths={[200, 320, 400]}
        sizes="(min-width: 768px) 220px, 160px"
        class="about-photo"
        loading="eager"
        decoding="async"
      />
      <div class="about-text">
        <p>
          I ran datacenters for nine years before joining Microsoft. That decade
          shaped how I think about reliability from the hardware up.
        </p>
        <p>
          Now I architect Azure Landing Zones, AKS Automatic, and AI Foundry
          deployments for Nordic enterprises. I use Terraform daily. The modules
          I ship come from real customer engagements, not theory.
        </p>
        <p>
          I co-founded two craft breweries. Fermentation and infrastructure both
          need the right controls and patience.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
